channel.title: BEATS FOR THE GRANNY WHIP - therealejoc [MULTI GENRE][BEAT TAPE]
channel.description:
Been a while since I put anything out, all beats were made in auxy. I decided to release a beat tape of the beats i'm planning on using for my official mixtape. Lots to choose from. "Smile!" and "Coffee." and "STEPS" are all finished tracks, meaning I do not plan to add additional lyrics. I know it's been a while since I've been around the forum, I got a new phone and mostly forgot about it until just now. Thanks anyways and enjoy!
[BEATS FOR THE GRANNY WHIP!](https://soundcloud.com/whoisejoc/sets/beats-for-the-granny-whip)
